# Theme switcher preview — cycles all 8 themes
Output .tmp/recordings/theme-switcher.gif
Output .tmp/recordings/theme-switcher.mp4
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 750
Set Padding 0
Hide
Type "bun demo/theme-preview.ts"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s
Show
Sleep 1.2s
Type "2" Sleep 1.2s
Type "3" Sleep 1.2s
Type "4" Sleep 1.2s
Type "5" Sleep 1.2s
Type "6" Sleep 1.2s
Type "7" Sleep 1.2s
Type "8" Sleep 1.2s
Type "1" Sleep 1.2s
Hide
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
